<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 叮！你有一个新的《故事》等待开启</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=214257278&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在宁夏固原西北55公里处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有这样一座<strong>“宝山”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200911/5f46f3611c304eb486faa3bdfd27744c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它是中国<strong>开凿最早</strong>的石窟之一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">距今已经<strong>1500</strong>多年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">堪与云冈石窟和龙门石窟媲美</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它开凿于<strong>北魏，至唐达到全盛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现存大小石窟<strong>162</strong>个、造像<strong>1000</strong>余尊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200911/7655f5a0adbd42b6a780de741918565f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它就是中国十大石窟之一的</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
